title: Ep272 Weird Torture
description:
This week, the gals get uncomfortable unpacking some tales of true terror. Topics include white rooms, non-consensual tickling, and one heck of a bug pit. Whip up a shrub to drown out the taste of Franzia Chillable Red, get the Queen's sign-off, and tune in for Weird Torture.

For a full list of show sponsors, visit https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
